      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，聚焦缓存场景下的用户行为。这个旅程需要分几个阶段？我初步理解应该有：进入网站、找到商品、实际撰写评价这三个主要环节？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section Enter online shop",
        "section Go to product",
        "section Write review"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，三个阶段很清晰。第一阶段\"Enter online shop\"包含访问网站和登录；第二阶段\"Go to product\"要体现用户导航到商品页、进入评价区、点击写评价按钮；第三阶段\"Write review\"就是填写标题、正文和提交。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Visit website",
        "Log in",
        "Navigate to product",
        "Go to Reviews section",
        "Click on \"Review\"",
        "Choose title",
        "Write text",
        "Submit review"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "每个步骤都需要打满意度分数吧？登录环节用户反馈一般，我给3分；浏览和导航类操作体验较好，给4分；最后的提交评价是关键转化点，建议给5分突出其重要性。这样分数梯度能反映用户情绪变化。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Log in: 3",
        "Visit website: 4",
        "Navigate to product: 4",
        "Go to Reviews section: 4",
        "Click on \"Review\": 4",
        "Choose title: 4",
        "Write text: 4",
        "Submit review: 5"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
